HULK SMASHES FROZEN CHARLOTTE ONCE AND FOR ALL!
The monstrous, ethereal, demonic/angelic Frozen Charlotte has plagued New Orleans for centuries, and it's high time to put a stop to it. And Hulk is just the guy to do it.Plus, Eldest makes another tempting offer to Bruce Banner...
